---
---

<section
  class="relative min-h-[85vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden bg-slate-deep text-surface-white"
>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <img
      alt="Грузовик на трассе"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40"
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1618582948377-cd7eb0e8cb14?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-deep via-slate-deep/80 to-transparent"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-container-max mx-auto px-md md:px-lg w-full py-xl">
    <div class="max-w-2xl space-y-lg">
      <div
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-xs px-sm py-1 bg-action-orange/20 border border-action-orange/30 rounded-full text-action-orange font-label-md"
      >
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-action-orange animate-pulse"></span>
        Международная логистика
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-display-lg text-display-lg leading-tight">
        Перевозка грузов <br /> по <span class="text-action-orange">ЧР и ЕС</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-surface-variant max-w-xl">
        Ваш надежный партнер в мире логистики. Безопасность, скорость и прозрачность на
        каждом этапе доставки.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-md">
        <a
          class="px-lg py-sm bg-action-orange text-white rounded-xl font-bold hover:scale-105 transition-transform flex items-center gap-xs"
          href="#quote"
        >
          Запросить стоимость
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
        </a>
        <a
          class="px-lg py-sm border border-surface-variant text-white rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-surface-white/10 transition-colors"
          href="#services">Наши услуги</a
        >
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-md pt-lg border-t border-surface-variant/20">
        <div>
          <div class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-action-orange">24/7</div>
          <div class="font-label-sm text-label-sm opacity-70">Поддержка</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-action-orange">8+</div>
          <div class="font-label-sm text-label-sm opacity-70">Стран ЕС</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-action-orange">100%</div>
          <div class="font-label-sm text-label-sm opacity-70">Гарантия</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
